msgid "Shisen-Sho Mahjongg-like Tile Game"
msgstr "Shisen-Sho-kahelludo simila al Mahjongg"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.kshisen.appdata.xml:12
msgid ""
"KShisen is a solitaire-like game played using the standard set of Mahjong "
"tiles. Unlike Mahjong however, KShisen has only one layer of scrambled tiles."
msgstr ""
"KShisen estas solitaire-simila ludo ludita uzante la norman aron de Mahjong-"
"kaheloj. Male al Mahjong tamen, KShisen havas nur unu tavolon de miksitaj "
"kaheloj."

